# smack-clj

Smack-clj allows you to write simple jabber bots in idiomatic clojure by providing a lightweight wrapper around the [smack](http://www.igniterealtime.org/projects/smack/) library.

## Usage



See the src/smack_clj/examples directory for more useage examples.

